but it's on very friendly terms.

1035
00:59:47,920 --> 00:59:50,590
From now on, it's time to begin the Five Senses Matching.

1036
00:59:50,630 --> 00:59:51,630
Taste.

1037
00:59:51,790 --> 00:59:54,130
When a man and a woman's tastes align,

1038
00:59:54,660 --> 00:59:57,430
they set off to savor a magical culinary date.

1039
00:59:57,900 --> 01:00:00,230
This matching is first-come, first-served.

1040
01:00:00,370 --> 01:00:02,200
If someone is selected first,

1041
01:00:02,900 --> 01:00:05,710
- It will be marked as sold out. - My gosh.

1042
01:00:05,870 --> 01:00:07,509
- First come, first served? - I don't think...

1043
01:00:07,510 --> 01:00:09,879
I've been this nervous in a long time.

1044
01:00:09,880 --> 01:00:12,279
It was pretty nerve-wracking because we couldn't really tell...

1045
01:00:12,280 --> 01:00:14,680
who was choosing which one.

1046
01:00:14,750 --> 01:00:18,050
- So it was truly a gamble. - I only have two days...

1047
01:00:18,120 --> 01:00:19,320
to make the most of this opportunity.

1048
01:00:19,520 --> 01:00:22,820
Now, we'll reveal the Taste Mission Matching results.
